### Get All Tasks
GET {{TaskifyProject_HostAddress}}/api/tasks
Accept: application/json

### Get Task by ID
GET {{TaskifyProject_HostAddress}}/api/tasks/1
Accept: application/json

### Get Filtered Tasks (by Status - Pending)
GET {{TaskifyProject_HostAddress}}/api/tasks/filter?status=0&pageNumber=1&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json

### Get Filtered Tasks (by Priority - High)
GET {{TaskifyProject_HostAddress}}/api/tasks/filter?priority=2&pageNumber=1&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json

### Get Filtered Tasks (by Status and Priority)
GET {{TaskifyProject_HostAddress}}/api/tasks/filter?status=0&priority=2&pageNumber=1&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json

### Get Filtered Tasks (by Status - Completed)
GET {{TaskifyProject_HostAddress}}/api/tasks/filter?status=1&pageNumber=1&pageSize=10
Accept: application/json

### Update Task - Change Title and Status to Completed
PUT {{TaskifyProject_HostAddress}}/api/tasks/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated: Complete project documentation",
  "status": 1
}

### Update Task - Change Priority to High
PUT {{TaskifyProject_HostAddress}}/api/tasks/2
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "priority": 2
}

### Update Task - Mark as Completed
PUT {{TaskifyProject_HostAddress}}/api/tasks/3
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": 1
}

